{"tid":1843276,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「求入」真正支持醫護嘅方法","createTime":"2020-01-26T06:37:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-26T06:41:40.000Z","uid":299530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"48edf555b47564d4eee71ab4146f6974557bc873","tid":1843276,"uid":299530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T06:37:31.000Z","msg":"其實好多醫護朋友明點解要罷工，呢幾日亦都收到好多大家嘅支持。<br />\n<br />\n但係呢啲唔係佢地決定罷唔罷工嘅因素，最主要嘅因素係同業嘅支持同埋比佢地知道香港人唔係擺佢地上枱，自生自滅。<br />\n<br />\n大家可以做嘅有以下兩樣：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1.呼籲醫護朋友立即加入工會</span></span><br />\n可以fb洗板，可以whatsapp朋友，總之要令工會人數係工業行動前有顯著嘅上升。知道同業有人陪佢地共同進退，個心都定啲，會肯做多步。<br />\n工會fb link:<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/HA.EmployAlliance/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2FHA.EmployAlliance%2F&d=1bJdDSIrk6tBa%2BBM68SGeiWHaP8IcnP89ZPrefCyuoo%3D&h=11fa8d0a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/HA.EmployAlliance/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">2.如果醫護工會宣佈罷工日子，大家立即吹雞全民罷工</span></span><br />\n問下自己，支持醫護罷工同時敢唔敢自己罷工。唔好支持人地罷工但係自己罷工不了。我相信有大家行動去支持，會感動到更多醫護朋友加入罷工。<br />\n<br />\n最後，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">話我知你地敢唔敢同醫護朋友一齊共進退啊？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n希望全香港可以團結<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16a55aa4064da4d06a638635878812e797270071","tid":1843276,"uid":299530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T06:39:58.000Z","msg":"認同嘅請幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55f5753978f0696048599ff73e9b225136ef05bc","tid":1843276,"uid":299530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T06:40:43.000Z","msg":"大家要清楚做咩先可以幫到件事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35f4b63f5e13aa02eb5fe6de56b0d8757ff30dc6","tid":1843276,"uid":299530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":